title: Two Small White Ducks in Water
creator: manum app

extendedInfo.description: Two Small White Ducks in Water is a Live Wallpaper.After you have downloaded and installed it,  You need in order to set it  as a Live Wallpaper:- go to your home screen;- press the menu button on your device;- select "Wallpaper";- select "Live Wallpapers";- search and select for this Live Wallpaper"- select "Settings" to see the settings or select "Set wallpaper" to activate it.System Requirement:any phone that came with Android OS 2.0 or later should work fine. Anything that came with 1.5 / 1.6 may have problemsTags:Two Small White Ducks in Water  Live wallpapers Sky Blue butterfly animal black

reviews.comment: Very cute....please remove butterfly....I\'ll repurchase and give 5 stars. It\'s adorable but the butterfly ruins it. I\'d love to rebuy this.
